paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the gene expression profiles of BRCA1 and BRCA2 mutation carriers and BRCAX individuals, focusing on the impact of pathogenic and low clinical significance variants. No specific BRCA2 variants are detailed in terms of cDNA or protein notation.
